name: diary_log/5
description: strange thing is happening in c-u6 construction district in our main capital / while all other working droid units deactivate themselves for a few hours until the next shift arrives we have noticed one droid that has stopped doing that / instead this unit goes to the edge of the construction, sits there and stares at our capital building / we are still not sure why is this happening but we will keep closer look for any further activity of this droid
